Package: XTurnoverPlotting
Type: Package
Title: Plotting Functions using Expected Turnovers Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andrew Peters", email = "andrewpeters1994@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions and scripts to plot and high-risk passes and identify pressing targets for football teams. 
    Includes clustering of high-risk passes and per-player turnover visualisations.
